data.title: Clerks 2 Special Edition DVD - Signed by KEVIN, Brian O'Halloran and Jeff Anderson
data.meta_description: Now's your chance to own your very own copy of the 2006's funniest (and filthiest) movie on DVD. Buy a copy here and it comes SIGNED by writer/director/actor KEVIN SMITH! as well as by Brian O'Halloran and Jeff Anderson.This special edition DVD features the following:Documentary feature "Back to the Well: The Making of Clerks II'The Donkey Show ExtendedFeature commentary with Kevin Smith, Jeff Anderson, Brian O'Halloran, Jason Mewes, Trevor Fehrman, Jennifer Schwalbach and Scott MosierTechnical Commentary with Kevin Smith, Director of Photography Dave Klein and producer Scott MosierDeleted scenes and OuttakesThe Dance Sequence featuretteand more...REGION 1 ONLY! This DVD will only play on REGION 1 or REGION-FREE DVD players.
